<sec id="id-4a1957b0-231b-41fb-b0c1-fa6d817363c4"><title><bold><?fontoxml-change-addition-start author-id="8763689" change-id="18e7c3e3-3dd0-4401-fbd3-da3d39db5d00" timestamp="1656533907448"?>Description of the issue<?fontoxml-change-addition-end change-id="18e7c3e3-3dd0-4401-fbd3-da3d39db5d00"?></bold></title><p><?fontoxml-change-addition-start author-id="8763689" change-id="a59e5705-9663-4789-ca19-9879ee741d31" timestamp="1656533892885"?>Partnerships include all the informal, formal, occasional or long-term agreements between two or more organizations. Partnerships can be established with local, national or international organizations that work to promote gender equality<?fontoxml-change-addition-end change-id="a59e5705-9663-4789-ca19-9879ee741d31"?><?fontoxml-change-addition-start author-id="8848353" change-id="07a0d91d-dd83-491a-8315-068d89e6eab2" timestamp="1670261598138"?> and supply chain partners<?fontoxml-change-addition-end change-id="07a0d91d-dd83-491a-8315-068d89e6eab2"?><?fontoxml-change-addition-start author-id="8763689" change-id="889aec9f-d6f4-430f-ed87-38e170812b36" timestamp="1656533892885"?>. There are various forms of partnerships: tacit agreements, charters, conventions, sponsorship, etc.<?fontoxml-change-addition-end change-id="889aec9f-d6f4-430f-ed87-38e170812b36"?></p><p><?fontoxml-change-addition-start author-id="8763689" change-id="1a3724a2-5025-4e94-d9ef-b5dd189eaefb" timestamp="1656533892885"?>A partnership reflects the shared vision of the organizations and their desire to work together to achieve the same goal. Partnerships also demonstrate the commitment of an organization and its capacity to involve other external stakeholders.<?fontoxml-change-addition-end change-id="1a3724a2-5025-4e94-d9ef-b5dd189eaefb"?></p><p><?fontoxml-change-addition-start author-id="8763689" change-id="bc4f8b14-b9e9-46c6-b6c4-e8f3642fabe0" timestamp="1656536408026"?>Partnerships are one of the keys to the successful implementation of <?fontoxml-change-addition-end change-id="bc4f8b14-b9e9-46c6-b6c4-e8f3642fabe0"?><?fontoxml-change-deletion author-id="8848353" change-id="ecbed7ec-12ed-482f-fa03-658209181615" text="a gender equality plan" timestamp="1666857933529"?><?fontoxml-change-addition-start author-id="8848353" change-id="c30b5e7c-c23a-4143-d46c-38f05fe037a1" timestamp="1666857896207"?>an action plan on gender equality<?fontoxml-change-addition-end change-id="c30b5e7c-c23a-4143-d46c-38f05fe037a1"?><?fontoxml-change-addition-start author-id="8763689" change-id="ba706033-fe30-4e5f-9331-7e4569dfc7f1" timestamp="1656536408026"?> in an organization.<?fontoxml-change-addition-end change-id="ba706033-fe30-4e5f-9331-7e4569dfc7f1"?></p></sec>